{"tid":842223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【封鎖新疆？】停售22/10後火車票 傳中共要轉移大量維族人","createTime":"2018-09-30T06:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T10:46:26.000Z","uid":212249,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d227d02ecb7592c2f3557c162ab7475d9d0973ac","tid":842223,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"新疆會發生大事件？內地鐵道部門公佈，下月22日以後，往返新疆的鐵路列車，與及在新疆境內的火車車票，一律全部停駛，未有透露具體原因。內地網民質疑當局未提前預警之下，突然停止載客，可能與中共要將大量被關在「再教育營」的維吾爾族人秘密轉移有關。<br />\n<br />\n新疆媒體指，烏魯木齊鐵路局在10.1長假期間，新疆加開119列旅客列車，往伊寧、庫爾勒、阿克蘇、喀什、和田等方向的臥鋪車票都已售罄；可是烏魯木齊旅遊局卻突然以「旅客列車運行圖調整」為由，宣佈停售下月22日以後所有進出新疆，及新疆內部的鐵路車票，直至另行通告為止。<br />\n<br />\n在香港瀏覽內地鐵路訂票網站12306，下月21日從新疆首府烏魯木齊往其他城市，仍有少量車票，但從22日起，不論從烏魯木齊前往蘭州、西安、成都、北京、上海、廣州等地，均只顯示車次，但出發時間、剩票等全部都沒有顯示，在備註中則寫有「列車運行圖調整，暫停發售」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n突然停售車票的消息，讓不少人感到錯愕，有網民向鐵路部門查詢，得到的回覆只是「目前還沒有消息，恢復售票日期另行通知」，令到這次停售車票，顯得極為神秘，網上廣傳「新疆是否要出大事了」的消息。<br />\n<br />\n不少民眾將鐵路停售的消息，與聯合國人權小組指中共將數以百萬計維吾爾族人關在「再教育營」連在一起。在海外的維族人團體則指，中共計劃將大量維族人，轉移到其他省份，所以要徵用鐵路運輸。總部設在美國的對華援助協會指出，目前新疆的再教育營人滿為患，當局正設法分流，其中在新疆西北部的新源縣，本月中旬當局出動數百名全副武裝特警、50多部巴士，將逾3,000名維族人秘密轉移，期間全縣實行交通管制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/all/realtime/article/20180930/58740979\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fall%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58740979&d=SSZloJwmmMd1heVPKxflU6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e3207501\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fall%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58740979&h=770d61e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/all/realtime/article/20180930/58740979</a>"},{"pid":"3f74d57037838c3c231d7d601bc7093be52635bc","tid":842223,"uid":183758,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:38:33.000Z","msg":"食屎啦支那共產黨<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"b74879560eaf04d8051a9fbb93ee3fa21ae84b5d","tid":842223,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:41:43.000Z","msg":"納粹"},{"pid":"67afac164b6ded9a5ce74e5ee139ce5e33f59813","tid":842223,"uid":208722,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:42:49.000Z","msg":"奧斯威辛鐵路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24769477c1cf0df4e4ae379a09671c800f585854","tid":842223,"uid":26385,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"去「沖涼」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母啲國際組織平時唔係好撚惡架咩<br />\n做乜見到中共就腳都軟埋？"},{"pid":"bff314e07e97f0b8271df9859380030942fc551d","tid":842223,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:46:11.000Z","msg":"通晒天仲叫唔叫秘密轉移<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd2061535af23ccaf80ae4d2372bbf696a946b2","tid":842223,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:46:32.000Z","msg":"genocide is coming to town<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea596fd4f5c29bffff236cd3d81c4104c2b95679","tid":842223,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:58:41.000Z","msg":"其實維人有咩得罪左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d95471c9ef590ad0ab696058ff668bcf232e67c","tid":842223,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T08:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"